<section class="review-system-map" aria-label="评价分析 Agent 系统总览">
  <header class="system-hero">
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <span class="case-label">CASE STUDY</span>
      <span class="version-label">review-analysis-reporter · v4.2.1</span>
    </div>
    <h2>评价分析不是写一份总结，而是完成一条可验证的业务闭环</h2>
    <p>
      两张来源表先被统一成一个事实包，Agent 只负责基于事实写报告；日报发布并发送成功后，系统才允许回写处理状态。
    </p>
    <a
      class="project-link"
      href="https://github.com/apexcheng/review-analysis-reporter-skill"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noreferrer"
      aria-label="在 GitHub 查看评价分析报告员项目"
    >
      查看 GitHub 项目
      <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </a>
  </header>

  <div class="system-metrics" aria-label="系统关键能力">
    <article>
      <span>DATA SOURCES</span>
      <strong>2 张表</strong>
      <small>首次评价与追加评价统一分析</small>
    </article>
    <article>
      <span>REPORT MODES</span>
      <strong>2 种模式</strong>
      <small>日报与周期对比各自保持独立边界</small>
    </article>
    <article>
      <span>SOURCE OF TRUTH</span>
      <strong>1 个事实包</strong>
      <small>报告只能使用本次事实包中的信息</small>
    </article>
    <article class="metric-accent">
      <span>WRITEBACK GATE</span>
      <strong>发送成功后</strong>
      <small>日报确认群消息送达，才修改业务状态</small>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="system-flow" aria-label="评价分析主链路">
    <article class="flow-node source-node">
      <span class="node-index">01 · INPUT</span>
      <h3>两类评价来源</h3>
      <div class="source-list">
        <span>首次评价</span>
        <span>追加评价</span>
      </div>
      <p>不同内容字段、不同统计时间，先分别读取。</p>
    </article>

    <span class="flow-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>

    <article class="flow-node">
      <span class="node-index">02 · FACT</span>
      <h3>Python 事实引擎</h3>
      <p>字段映射、筛选、去重、统计，并输出统一 JSON 事实包。</p>
    </article>

    <span class="flow-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>

    <article class="flow-node">
      <span class="node-index">03 · NARRATIVE</span>
      <h3>Agent 生成报告</h3>
      <p>不重判情绪，不补充外部事实，只把事实包整理成可读结论。</p>
    </article>

    <span class="flow-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>

    <article class="flow-node">
      <span class="node-index">04 · DELIVERY</span>
      <h3>文档与群消息</h3>
      <p>报告先落盘，再发布在线文档，并发送到业务群。</p>
    </article>

    <span class="flow-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>

    <article class="flow-node gate-node">
      <span class="node-index">05 · STATE</span>
      <h3>状态回写闸门</h3>
      <p>日报 Webhook 成功才按来源表回写；发送失败则保留原状态。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <footer class="system-rule">
    <span>核心边界</span>
    <strong>模型负责解释事实，脚本负责固定口径，日报发送结果决定能不能改变业务状态。</strong>
  </footer>
</section>

